snippet.title: Slendytubbies 2D - v1.5 Update (NEW MAPS & MORE!)
snippet.description:
SLENDYTUBBIES 2D Just got a BIG UPDATE to v1.5!

This version has many improvements; featuring new maps, monsters & a new master server (no more server select or "server is full" errors)!
DOWNLOAD NOW FOR PC/MAC/ANDROID:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ZeoWorks.S2DMultiplayer

(Note that the iOS edition will be released sometime late this week, this is due to how apple accepts submissions.)
